channel.description: I just have a quick queston on why JDK 6u26 doesn't work for my client. It doesn't work for either the compiler or the run, yet it works just fine in the source. I'm using jdk 6 because 7 doesn't allow you to make working webclients unless people are using java 7, and not everyone is using java 7...
